{"type": "article", "id": 59160, "title": "一款自带热点的卷轴月历，告别翻页撕毁体验｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-10T22:45:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54965, "name": "JIHE STUDIO"}, {"id": 54966, "name": "Brandson Equipment"}, {"id": 54967, "name": "ExcitingPR"}, {"id": 54968, "name": "Moreno Schweikle"}, {"id": 54969, "name": "Janne Schimmel"}, {"id": 54970, "name": "李天"}, {"id": 54971, "name": "Claudius Dreyer"}, {"id": 31306, "name": "Kevin Chiam"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 241, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181210200056riu6lbV8cf2YMw4E.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>2019 热点日历 by ExcitingPR</h3><p>按照设计师的说法，传播业有两大痛点：适度的安排与及时的热点。这是热点月历 1.0 的诞生初衷。今年的 2.0 版本，ExcitingPR 延续了前作的精华，并做了一些大胆的尝试，让它有用、有趣还有品。</p><p>它可能是首款不间断、可转动的台历，摒弃古典式台历的使用方式，以别具一格的转动方式，告别翻页或撕毁的传统体验。设计师希望你能通过转动，感受生命流淌，收集岁月印记。</p><p>精挑细选的 238 个热点，长 2.81 米。此外，设计师还从每月的几十个热点中，甄选 2 个作详细介绍。它保留古典月历的排版，并标注出节气、周数。背面的整块纤维板，使书写毫无压力，轻松创造专属于你的办公、生活小助手。售价 138 元，<a href=\"https://weidian.com/item.html?itemID=2623096487&amp;spider_token=cea4&amp;spider=seller.zx-shopdetail.5.1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200246beZaFLodKVAWJpT9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562674\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200324XIHNo6w0AKYMefhq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200325YhSuyBKnD9vtPeJp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102003273rxdJFGhlsOqwV46.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641631\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200326y2HbElzv4j3XWsK9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102003257Fl32y6ZNMGkAdSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200328CjVt3yqADInREcUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200331V3gEm2HQP9hanklA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Moment Pen by Kevin Chiam</h3><p>笔和纸一般情况下都是同时出现的，这款名为 Moment Pen 的笔恰好把纸和笔结合了起来。在需要的时候，人们可以从笔体上撕下单独的备忘录纸，背面粘上胶水。可以随时使用，随时粘贴。</p><p>这是设计师 Kevin Chiam 的创意，一款“卷在笔上的便利贴 ”。有了它随身只要带着这支笔就可以了，需要记录一些文字提示，或者与别人交换信息和想法时只要从笔上剥下便利贴，就可以马上开始写了。即使在家中也不会发生需要给家人留言时，找到便利贴但找不到笔，有笔的时候又找不到便利贴的情况。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121020035948t96aEFdngW7C3Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121020040010fnEFuq8C9tZRIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200400bdPr6iK980Tm57p3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200359mt25kIp3oYE4qedh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102003591A8YF3dBS9WCnegX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/12/06/stickies-on-a-roll/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Brandson Alarm Clocks by Claudius Dreyer for Brandson Equipment</h3><p>这是设计师 Claudius Dreyer 为品牌 Brandson Equipment 量身而作的一款时钟，它的设计包含了使用者对传统闹钟所期望的所有功能，并且具有投射时间的附加功能。</p><p>使用者可以转动顶部安装的刻度盘来调整内置投影仪系统的位置，以适应用户可能将其远离墙壁的不同距离。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200443bZF0ceCD6qWl1yX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200443Zk2tHl4ux05qJLdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102004437IQr2EbGY5efHFAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200444HNmdxQ8Fqow0OsIE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121020044405JFpVfH8sMtvwIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200445Uj1OyoQbgDiFRp75.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102004444aDgAEdWVfo3ZyzY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102004469butyW4lnJp0fHhr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121020044624rGHAa6ERFPbk3D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200445wMVTqvJD3QrHCLa6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.claudiusdreyer.com/#/brandson/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Claudius Dreyer</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Pinji Table by Tony Lee</h3><p>新锐设计师李天创立的工作室 JIHE STUDIO（几何原本） 是一家多元化设计工作室，他擅长运用简约的点线面构建美好的产品设计。</p><p>这款名为 Pinji 的边桌采用了不平衡的设计，让人看了感觉要翻倒，但大可不必担心，它的重心在底部也非常稳固。生活中，我们一定遇到过不小心把桌子上的花瓶碰掉，设计师巧妙的将花瓶和边桌作结合，这非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200522JPTDqah6z7e9wOjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571777\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812102005225sPjlO0qm4H8Jv3W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.445390\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200522KlPwpLHz87302ZRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200523pgaRZo8scwjrAftC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.570801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200544HZAD8Nqa6sJWey5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.572000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.jihestudio.com/?post_type=products&amp;page_id=9824\" rel=\"nofollow\">JIHE STUDIO</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Return To Default by Moreno Schweikle and Janne Schimmel</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Moreno Schweikle 和 Janne Schimmel，突破标准家具的尺寸，制作出漫画版本的办公家具系列 Return To Default 。</p><p>Return To Default 系列包括三把椅子，每把椅子都是基于标准办公椅，经过拉伸、扩展或倍增，形成一个新形式。</p><p>书桌椅被拉伸成为一个三人沙发，会议椅成为一个软垫扶手椅和办公室凳子结合起来创造成一个巨大的休闲椅。这些设计是两位设计师使用 3D 软件实验出来的结果。</p><p>“对我们来说，办公室似乎是一个可以找到许多原型设计的地方，因此办公空间通常被视为视觉上相对枯燥的景观，”他们说。“办公椅已经成为日常和高效的标志。通过扩展其功能，我们希望打破办公空间的单调景观。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200615zWxpBa9dwetrqClV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200616HKsqJhbIgPt76Y4D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181210200617rLKCioT0POaWRdFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121020061632THUBlwgNVj9kpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/12/09/schimmel-schweikle-return-to-default-office-furniture-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}